  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      morbidity after tonsillictomy remains asignificant problem therefore they recommend
      prophylactic antibiotics to reduce it.in the other hand, the overuse of antimicrobial agents
      can lead to antimicrobial resistance ,adverse drug events,and unnecessary cost.so,the
      effectiveness and necessity of antibiotic following tonsillictomy needs to be studied .
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
